<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Quittance de loyer</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: DejaVu Sans, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #333; margin: 40px; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 5px; }
        .header p { margin: 0; color: #666; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .section h2 { font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .label { color: #666; }
        .amount { font-weight: bold; }
        .total { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; border-top: 2px solid #333; padding-top: 10px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 10px; color: #999; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 15px; }
        .badge { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px; }
        .parties { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; }
        .partie { flex: 1; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; }
        .partie h3 { font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 8px; color: #555; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>QUITTANCE DE LOYER</h1>
        <p>Colocation.com – Gestion locative</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="parties">
            <div class="partie">
                <h3>BAILLEUR</h3>
                {% if quittance.loyer.colocation.proprietaire is defined %}
                <strong>{{ quittance.loyer.colocation.proprietaire.nomComplet }}</strong><br>
                {{ quittance.loyer.colocation.adresse }}<br>
                {{ quittance.loyer.colocation.codePostal }} {{ quittance.loyer.colocation.ville }}
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="partie">
                <h3>LOCATAIRE</h3>
                {% if quittance.loyer.chambre.locataire is defined %}
                <strong>{{ quittance.loyer.chambre.locataire.nomComplet }}</strong><br>
                {{ quittance.loyer.colocation.adresse }}<br>
                {{ quittance.loyer.colocation.codePostal }} {{ quittance.loyer.colocation.ville }}
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>BIEN LOUÉ</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Colocation :</span>
            <span>{{ quittance.loyer.colocation.nom }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Chambre :</span>
            <span>{{ quittance.loyer.chambre.nom }} ({{ quittance.loyer.chambre.surface }} m²)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Période :</span>
            <span>{{ quittance.periodeDebut|date('d/m/Y') }} au {{ quittance.periodeFin|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>DÉTAIL DU PAIEMENT</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Loyer nu :</span>
            <span class="amount">{{ quittance.montantLoyer }}€</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Charges :</span>
            <span class="amount">{{ quittance.montantCharges }}€</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row total">
            <span>TOTAL RÉGLÉ :</span>
            <span>{{ quittance.montantTotal }}€</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <p>
            Je soussigné(e), bailleur du logement désigné ci-dessus, déclare avoir reçu de
            <strong>{% if quittance.loyer.chambre.locataire is defined %}{{ quittance.loyer.chambre.locataire.nomComplet }}{% endif %}</strong>
            la somme de <strong>{{ quittance.montantTotal }}€</strong> ({{ quittance.montantTotal|number_format(2) }} euros)
            au titre du loyer et des charges du mois de <strong>{{ quittance.periodeDebut|date('F Y') }}</strong>,
            et lui en donne quittance, sous réserve de tous mes droits.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: right;">
        <p>Fait le {{ quittance.genereeAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #999; padding-top: 5px; display: inline-block; min-width: 200px;">
            Signature du bailleur
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Document généré automatiquement par Colocation.com – {{ quittance.genereeAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
